> install git
> to check whether its installed
	git --version
> pwd 
	gives the present working directory
> ls -la
	lists all the files along with hidden files
> ls
	lists all the files (not hidden)
> to initialize
	git init
> to get the current status
	git status
----------
> to configure an account
	git config --global user.name "yourName(username of your github)"
	git config --global user.email "your email(email of your github)"
> to see the list of config
	git config --list							